OJ 1990 L 225, p. 1
), as amended by the Act concerning the conditions of accession of the Kingdom of Norway, the Republic of Austria, the Republic of Finland and the Kingdom of Sweden (
OJ 1994 C 241, p. 21
), as adjusted by Decision 95/1/EC, Euratom, ECSC of the Council of the European Union of 1 January 1995 (
OJ 1995 L 1, p. 1
) (‘the Merger Directive’), and Article 49 TFEU.

